    "Schools with limited budgets or short staff might face challenges in taking advantage of the resources offered through Chat-GPT.",
    "Similarly, using Gen-AI will require new tools, such as efficient processing systems and reliable internet connections.",
    "This means that universities that do not have sufficient resources cannot benefit from the advantages of LLM.Although universities have the opportunity to do this, they may still face resistance when implementing changes.",
    "Employers, managers, and academic staff may prefer traditional courses.",
    "Recent research suggests that ChatGPT in classroom planning and assessment can yield significant improvements [130].Additionally, efforts will be made to provide training and facilitate information sharing among key stakeholders, such as teachers and students, to improve their understanding and knowledge of female students."
